DBIx-SimpleGoBetween version 0.01
=================================

Super simple DBI instance wrapper, thats intended to act as a quick
shortcut for small result sets.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
    # to run extended tests against your mysql database
    # set the following variables
    export TEST_HOST='your_target_host'
    export TEST_DB='your_target_test_database'
    export TEST_USER='your test user'
    export TEST_PASSWORD='your test password';
    # you will also need the following module(s) installed
     DBI,DBD::mysql,DBIx::BulkLoader::Mysql
     Not to mention have a working mysql database
   
   make install

